  }, "Unsplash")), mdx("p", null, "The casual onlooker might assume I landed the first job I applied for, my pride would probably prefer that to be the case. It wouldn't be true however, and it also wouldn't be much to write about."), mdx("p", null, "Before we go too deep, a bit more about me. I have worked in multiple different sectors and disciplines over the years. The one common feature of my previous employers up until now is that they have all been geographically close to where I live. There weren't many ", mdx("a", {
    parentName: "p",
